e Express\" || [[Franconia\u2013Springfield station]] ||  || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || \n|-\n| 340 || Patriot Ridge \u2013 Saratoga || [[Franconia\u2013Springfield station]] || Fort Belvoir (North Area) || {{X mark big}} || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || \n|-\n| 341 || Boston Boulevard \u2013 Saratoga || [[Franconia\u2013Springfield station]] || Saratoga Park & Ride || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || \n|-\n| 371 || Lorton \u2013 Franconia-Springfield Metro || [[Franconia\u2013Springfield station]] || Lorton Park & Ride || {{X mark big}} || {{Check mark}} || {{Check mark}} || {{Check mark}} || \n|-\n| 372 || Lorton \u2013 Alban Road || [[Franconia\u2013Springfield station]] || Lorton Park & Ride || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || \n|-\n| 373 || Lorton \u2013 Fullerton Road || [[Franconia\u2013Springfield station]] || Laurel Crest Drive & Silverbrook Road || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || \n|-\n| 393 || Saratoga \u2013 Mark Center \u2013 Pentagon Express || Saratoga Park & Ride || [[Pentagon station]] || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || AM Service to Pentagon, PM Service to Saratoga\nExpress Route: $4.25 Fare\n|-\n| 394 || Saratoga \u2013 Pentagon Express || Saratoga Shopping Center (Rolling Road) (AM Start)\nBacklick North Park & Ride (PM End)\n| [[Pentagon station]] || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || AM Service to Pentagon, PM Service to Backlick North\nExpress Route: $4.25 Fare\n|-\n| 395 || Gambrill \u2013 Pentagon Express || Gambrill Park & Ride (AM Start)\nBacklick North Park & Ride (PM End) \n| [[Pentagon station]] || {{Check mark}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || {{X mark big}} || AM Service to Pentagon, PM Service to Backlick North\nExpress Route: $4.25 Fare\n|-\n| 401 || Backlick \u2013 